OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776715554
OL,3,CTrial for two men accused over young
OL,4,Cmum's death at caravan site
OL,6,FTwo men are due to go on trial accused
OL,7,Fof being involved in the death of a
OL,8,Fmother-of-one who was found dead at a
OL,9,Fcaravan park in Nottinghamshire.
OL,11,FDonatas Noreika and Arturas Karvelis
OL,12,Fhave both been charged with conspiring
OL,13,Fto prevent the lawful and decent
OL,14,Fburial of a body in relation to the
OL,15,Fdeath of Orinta Narbtaite in the early
OL,16,Fhours of 20 March this year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776715554
OL,3,CTrial for two men accused over young
OL,4,Cmum's death at caravan site
OL,6,FAssisted by a Lithuanian interpreter,
OL,7,Fneither man was asked to enter any
OL,8,Fpleas to the charge when they appeared
OL,9,Ffrom custody at Nottingham Crown Court
OL,10,Ftoday.
OL,12,FA number of members of Ms Narbtaite's
OL,13,Ffamily were in court to hear Judge
OL,14,FSteven Coupland set a provisional
OL,15,Ftrial date of 7 September with a three-
OL,16,Fweek time estimate.
OL,18,FFollowing her death, her family
OL,19,Freleased a tribute for the 32-year-
OL,20,Fold, describing her as a "devoted and
OL,21,Floving mother".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776715554
OL,3,CTrial for two men accused over young
OL,4,Cmum's death at caravan site
OL,6,FThe tribute reads: "It is with
OL,7,Fprofound sorrow that we announce the
OL,8,Fpassing of Orinta Narbutaite, a
OL,9,Fcherished member of our community
OL,10,Fwhose kindness, dignity, and warmth
OL,11,Fleft a lasting impression on all who
OL,12,Fknew her.
OL,14,F"Orinta will be remembered not only
OL,15,Ffor her compassionate nature and quiet
OL,16,Fstrength, but also for the genuine
OL,17,Fcare and respect she showed to others.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776715554
OL,3,CTrial for two men accused over young
OL,4,Cmum's death at caravan site
OL,6,F"She had a remarkable ability to offer
OL,7,Fcomfort and support, and her presence
OL,8,Fbrought a sense of calm and
OL,9,Freassurance to those around her.
OL,11,F"A devoted and loving mother to her
OL,12,Fdaughter"
OL,14,F"Above all, Orinta was a devoted and
OL,15,Floving mother to her daughter, whom
OL,16,Fshe cherished deeply. Her love,
OL,17,Fguidance, and dedication as a parent
OL,18,Fwill remain a lasting part of her
OL,19,Flegacy.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776715554
OL,3,CTrial for two men accused over young
OL,4,Cmum's death at caravan site
OL,6,F"Orinta Narbutaite will be deeply
OL,7,Fmissed and forever remembered. Her
OL,8,Fmemory will continue to live on in the
OL,9,Fhearts of all who had the privilege of
OL,10,Fknowing her."
OL,12,FA murder investigation was launched
OL,13,Ffollowing the discovery of Ms
OL,14,FNarbutaite's body last month.
OL,16,FPolice had cordoned off a bungalow at
OL,17,Fthe Longbow Residential Park as part
OL,18,Fof the investigation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776715554
OL,3,CTrial for two men accused over young
OL,4,Cmum's death at caravan site
OL,6,FNoreika, 37, of Main Street, Milton,
OL,7,Fand 45-year-old Karvelis, of Broad
OL,8,FStreet, Parkgate, Rotherham - who is
OL,9,Falso known within the community as
OL,10,FArturas Bockus - were both remanded
OL,11,Finto custody until May 22.
OL,13,FA 64-year-old man and a 60-year-old
OL,14,Fwoman who were also arrested have
OL,15,Fsince been released without charge.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776715554
OL,3,CTrial for two men accused over young
OL,4,Cmum's death at caravan site
OL,6,FNottinghamshire Police has also
OL,7,Fpreviously confirmed it referred the
OL,8,Fcase to the Independent Office for
OL,9,FPolice Conduct, the police watchdog,
OL,10,Fdue to past involvement with Ms
OL,11,FNarbutaite.
OL,13,FIn a statement released shortly after
OL,14,Fthe discovery of her body, Detective
OL,15,FInspector Matt Scott said: "Our
OL,16,Fthoughts remain with Orinta's family
OL,17,Fand friends, who have asked for
OL,18,Fprivacy at what must be an extremely
OL,19,Fdifficult time.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
